{"tid":2451013,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"科興第二針下周五開打 專家憂死亡恐慌爆棄針潮 群體免疫落空","createTime":"2021-03-17T21:37:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-18T05:56:02.000Z","uid":130626,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"fa47ec7c71d17e805a5e064a5dc64a4f4d51eb64","tid":2451013,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T21:37:50.000Z","msg":"科興疫苗自上月26日開打至今，累計有25.4萬人接種，最快下周五（26日）要再打第二針。然而接種科興疫苗後屢現不良反應個案，專家擔心如市民未如期接種第二針科興疫苗，將影響群體免疫效果。專家又提醒，如接種首劑後首出現過敏包括「出風癩」反應人士，都應暫緩接種，個別個案或可考慮轉打另一款疫苗，惟須視乎政府能否安排。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210318/BBQTKWYEWJFIXBB5W234CCSALY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210318%2FBBQTKWYEWJFIXBB5W234CCSALY%2F&d=1mBOIAkAA7%2FwaZBThmus2dVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=197adbb9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210318%2FBBQTKWYEWJFIXBB5W234CCSALY%2F&h=43ca6c07\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210318/BBQTKWYEWJFIXBB5W234CCSALY/</a>"},{"pid":"9316909dbd8eaec3134fa42f63459a7fe8f3bc8e","tid":2451013,"uid":250308,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T21:39:23.000Z","msg":"唔打第二針咪罰款"},{"pid":"6e1428f2d4331ec01ca9aa8ee1160e75e059fac8","tid":2451013,"uid":7043,"like":60,"dislike":0,"score":60,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T21:40:23.000Z","msg":"打左有紀錄嫁嘛<br />\n邊個契弟唔打第二針<br />\n咪國安法拉佢老母臭閪囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c602b11cf492bcb9a6fd36407b63f11bc802e839","tid":2451013,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T21:51:24.000Z","msg":"&quot;Jerk&quot; immunity"},{"pid":"d711a0bd827a64c4f75b77e377b81e6f49fe94bc","tid":2451013,"uid":70786,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T21:55:33.000Z","msg":"林鄭同班狗官仲唔打鑼打鼓咁打科興第二針？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c5e994ecd1e9324015be6dead702